.SH NAME
.PP
s1kd\-fmgen \- Generate front matter data module contents
.SH SYNOPSIS
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
s1kd\-fmgen\ [\-D\ <TYPE>]\ [\-F\ <FMTYPES>]\ [\-I\ <date>]\ [\-P\ <PM>]
\ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ [\-p\ <name>=<val>\ ...]\ [\-t\ <TYPE>]\ [\-x\ <XSL>]
